All right, Ryan was part
of an online trend

28:54.066 --> 28:55.835
known as the Junkies
of PicThread.

28:55.868 --> 28:58.437
Users post photos
glamorizing their drug use.

28:58.470 --> 29:00.506
RYAN: Sasha wanted
to teach him a lesson,

29:00.539 --> 29:03.542
just like she did with Pastor
Harrison and Nicole Hogan.

29:03.575 --> 29:06.312
She wanted to make examples
of them on social media.

29:06.345 --> 29:08.915
Linking them all together with
the hashtag "Graphic Warning."

29:08.948 --> 29:11.918
I still can't believe
that Sasha's the target.

29:11.951 --> 29:13.252
She seemed so normal, right?

29:13.285 --> 29:15.487
Well, she must be
extremely damaged

29:15.521 --> 29:17.489
from her time
as a content moderator.

29:17.523 --> 29:19.191
You know,
in jobs like that,

29:19.225 --> 29:21.828
it's not unusual
to have chronic PTSD.

29:21.861 --> 29:23.162
It's similar to what

29:23.195 --> 29:25.031
combat veterans experience.

29:25.064 --> 29:28.000
It's very rare to have
a female serial killer.

29:28.034 --> 29:31.570
They're usually
not this violent.

29:31.603 --> 29:33.272
In her mind, she believes

29:33.305 --> 29:36.075
that she's not doing this
for her own enjoyment.

29:36.108 --> 29:38.310
She's a vigilante.

29:38.344 --> 29:41.180
She really thinks
she's making the Internet safer.

29:41.213 --> 29:42.849
So maybe that's
her Graphic Warning:

29:42.882 --> 29:44.150
post photos like these,

29:44.183 --> 29:45.517
you could be next.

29:45.551 --> 29:48.520
*

29:48.554 --> 29:50.522
(panting)

29:50.556 --> 29:52.291
SASHA: You went to
this boy's funeral

29:52.324 --> 29:54.861
just to snap this photo.

30:01.567 --> 30:03.903
Sometimes I wonder what
you people are thinking

30:03.936 --> 30:05.371
when you post
stuff like this.

30:05.404 --> 30:07.339
I really do.

30:07.373 --> 30:09.241
Wh... What are
you gonna...

30:09.275 --> 30:10.943
what are you
gonna do to me?

30:12.411 --> 30:15.081
I'm teaching you a lesson, Toby.

30:15.114 --> 30:17.950
I'm teaching
everyone a lesson.

30:17.984 --> 30:19.118
What is this?

30:19.151 --> 30:20.853
W-Why are you doing this?

30:20.887 --> 30:21.620
Wha... Ah!

30:21.653 --> 30:23.856
(screams, sobs)

30:25.291 --> 30:26.558
Please...

30:26.592 --> 30:28.895
P-Please...

30:28.928 --> 30:30.863
Please, don't...

30:30.897 --> 30:32.064
(screaming)

30:34.200 --> 30:36.168
(gasping)

30:36.202 --> 30:38.437
(sobbing)

30:38.470 --> 30:39.838
(screams)

30:43.675 --> 30:45.411
Huh?
Oh, you got that?

30:45.444 --> 30:46.879
Oh, no.
I can't believe
this is happening again.

30:46.913 --> 30:48.180
I know!
All right,
it wasn't me this time.

30:49.481 --> 30:51.283
KRUMTIZ: It's a photo of
our junkie, Ryan Kilmer.

30:51.317 --> 30:52.885
Posted to his account.

30:52.919 --> 30:54.053
We didn't scan the QR code,

30:54.086 --> 30:55.387
so Sasha must have posted this.

30:55.421 --> 30:58.024
What stopping her from
just posting the next photo?

30:58.057 --> 30:59.091
Because there isn't one.

31:00.459 --> 31:03.262
I got behind the site
from her last QR code,

31:03.295 --> 31:05.497
and the next message is
"Please Don't Feed the Trolls,"

31:05.531 --> 31:08.000
but... there's no photo.

31:08.034 --> 31:10.970
Sasha's clues
have different themes,

31:11.003 --> 31:12.939
but each one has
a signature photo.

31:12.972 --> 31:14.941
So why doesn't this one
have a photo?

31:17.176 --> 31:18.177
(phone buzzes)

31:18.210 --> 31:20.212
Agent Mundo.

31:20.246 --> 31:22.381
(sirens wailing in distance)

31:22.414 --> 31:24.350
Yes, Cal Mundo is my father.
Why?

31:34.526 --> 31:36.228
Hi.

31:36.262 --> 31:38.364
Nina, what the hell
are you doing here?

31:38.397 --> 31:39.698
Where's Devon?

31:39.731 --> 31:42.001
They said my wife was here.

31:42.034 --> 31:43.402
I had to tell 'em
I was your wife

31:43.435 --> 31:44.670
so they'd let me stay
with your father.

31:44.703 --> 31:46.939
Stay? Wha...

31:46.973 --> 31:49.008
What were you doing with him
in the first place?

31:49.041 --> 31:50.977
I saved
your father's life, Elijah.

31:51.010 --> 31:53.079
He came to see me.

31:53.112 --> 31:54.947
Why?

31:54.981 --> 31:56.182
I don't know.

31:56.215 --> 31:58.117
To talk, maybe?

31:58.150 --> 32:00.586
I'm a pretty good listener.

32:00.619 --> 32:02.588
Well, you used to
think so, anyway.

32:02.621 --> 32:04.123
He said you
told him about me.

32:05.691 --> 32:08.660
He was not very
friendly at first.

32:08.694 --> 32:11.230
But then we started talking...

32:11.263 --> 32:14.266
getting to know each other.

32:14.300 --> 32:16.468
We were actually
having a really nice time.

32:16.502 --> 32:18.537
And then, out of nowhere,
he just collapsed

32:18.570 --> 32:20.672
and I had to give him CPR
until the paramedics came.

32:20.706 --> 32:23.575
They said he might not have
made it had I not done that.

32:26.345 --> 32:29.281
I'm sorry, Elijah.

32:29.315 --> 32:31.984
I know how hard
this must be for you.

32:37.023 --> 32:38.724
Nina, listen to me

32:38.757 --> 32:40.692
very carefully.

32:40.726 --> 32:43.062
I'm having you banned
from this hospital

32:43.095 --> 32:44.997
and then I am filing
a restraining order.

32:45.031 --> 32:47.066
If you call or text

32:47.099 --> 32:50.469
or come within 50 feet
of anyone in my family--

32:50.502 --> 32:52.604
anyone-- you will be arrested.

32:52.638 --> 32:54.640
Do you understand?

32:55.741 --> 32:57.743
I'm an agent with the FBI.

32:59.545 --> 33:01.513
Don't test me.

33:01.547 --> 33:03.582
I'm just trying to help you.

33:03.615 --> 33:05.184
That's all I've ever
wanted to do-- I just...

33:05.217 --> 33:06.752
I don't want your help!

33:06.785 --> 33:09.388
I want you to leave.

33:11.290 --> 33:14.426
Stay out of my life!

33:25.104 --> 33:26.038
(sighs)

33:30.109 --> 33:32.044
Well, we know that Sasha
is in Boston.
RUSSELL: Right.

33:32.078 --> 33:34.713
She's not gonna stop
until her message is complete.

33:34.746 --> 33:37.116
Right, and we know
the next sin is Trolling.

33:37.149 --> 33:40.652
But with no photo, that could
mean there's no victim yet.

33:40.686 --> 33:43.255
Could be staging
her next murder as we speak.

33:43.289 --> 33:46.125
Actually, that could be
how we find her.

33:46.158 --> 33:47.659
Raven, uh,

33:47.693 --> 33:50.229
log onto Sasha's
PicThread account.

33:50.262 --> 33:51.630
Then click onto "followers"

33:51.663 --> 33:53.799
and go to the "people
you may know" section.

33:55.301 --> 33:57.803
Social media sites like
FriendAgenda and PicThread--

33:57.836 --> 34:00.072
they use this,
uh, proximity-based

34:00.106 --> 34:01.373
algorithm, right?
RAVEN: Right.

34:01.407 --> 34:03.842
To determine who shows up
in this section.

34:03.875 --> 34:05.611
They actually
suggest people

34:05.644 --> 34:08.747
that you have
physically been around.

34:08.780 --> 34:11.183
I downloaded the, uh,
PicThread app this morning

34:11.217 --> 34:13.252
just to check it out.
Okay, so I have

34:13.285 --> 34:14.220
zero followers, right?

34:14.253 --> 34:16.855
So if I go to my

34:16.888 --> 34:18.657
"people you may know" section,

34:18.690 --> 34:21.127
(chuckling):
then...

34:21.160 --> 34:22.060
(laughing): Oh...

34:22.861 --> 34:24.763
Look at all of 'em.

34:24.796 --> 34:26.132
And you, who are standing

34:26.165 --> 34:27.233
right next to me,

34:27.266 --> 34:28.700
are number one
on my list.

34:28.734 --> 34:30.436
She was physically near

34:30.469 --> 34:33.705
all of her victims while she was
staging their murders.

34:33.739 --> 34:35.607
All right, so they would
show up in that section.

34:35.641 --> 34:36.875
Yeah, already on it.

34:36.908 --> 34:40.179
Pastor Harrison.

34:40.212 --> 34:41.813
Nicole Hogan.

34:41.847 --> 34:42.881
Ryan Kilmer.

34:42.914 --> 34:45.551
So in order to figure out
who Sasha's

34:45.584 --> 34:48.120
Trolling victim might be,
we need to...

34:48.154 --> 34:49.688
All we need to do is cross-
reference the PicThread users

34:49.721 --> 34:51.290
in the Boston area
who have been flagged

34:51.323 --> 34:53.692
for trolling... with the users

34:53.725 --> 34:55.861
of Sasha's
"people you may know."

34:55.894 --> 34:57.563
Toby Allen.

34:57.596 --> 34:59.398
Sasha's
next victim.

34:59.431 --> 35:02.134
You guys, his phone is on.

35:02.168 --> 35:03.635
We have his location.

35:03.669 --> 35:04.636
It's an abandoned theater.

35:04.670 --> 35:06.205
And Sasha might be

35:06.238 --> 35:07.273
right there with him.

35:09.741 --> 35:11.610
Now, I'll only be gone
a couple of hours,

35:11.643 --> 35:14.813
but it's very important
that you see every photo.

35:14.846 --> 35:17.916
You can't miss one.
That's the job.

35:17.949 --> 35:19.851
You look away for a
second and you can

35:19.885 --> 35:21.920
miss something
that gets posted.

35:21.953 --> 35:24.156
(muffled grunting)

35:24.190 --> 35:26.192
Don't go anywhere, okay?

35:26.225 --> 35:27.226
(grunting)

35:38.870 --> 35:42.708
Toby, are you enjoying
those photos?

35:42.741 --> 35:43.942
No!

35:43.975 --> 35:46.345
RYAN:
Sasha, freeze! FBI!

35:46.378 --> 35:47.679
Put the gun down!

35:48.880 --> 35:51.717
Wow, I'm impressed.

35:51.750 --> 35:53.785
How the hell did
you find me here?

35:53.819 --> 35:55.687
We found Toby Allen.

35:55.721 --> 35:58.490
He's now safely in our custody.

35:58.524 --> 36:00.859
It's over, Sasha.
You will not harm

36:00.892 --> 36:02.794
another innocent person.

36:03.795 --> 36:04.763
Innocent?

36:04.796 --> 36:06.732
A man preaching hate

36:06.765 --> 36:09.268
instead of love?

36:09.301 --> 36:12.571
A woman so full of herself
she documents everything,

36:12.604 --> 36:13.839
no matter how indecent?

36:13.872 --> 36:17.243
A heroin addict
glorifying his disease

36:17.276 --> 36:18.777
and recruiting
other users?

36:19.845 --> 36:21.880
And this one...

36:21.913 --> 36:24.650
worst of all.

36:24.683 --> 36:26.452
An Internet Troll

36:26.485 --> 36:29.621
who taunts depressed teens
into committing suicide,

36:29.655 --> 36:31.690
then posts doctored photos
mocking them

36:31.723 --> 36:34.626
on their own memorial sites.
How sick is that?

36:34.660 --> 36:36.528
It's wrong.

36:36.562 --> 36:39.265
It's illegal and immoral.

36:39.298 --> 36:41.667
But Sasha...

36:41.700 --> 36:44.270
what you've done
is so much worse.

36:45.604 --> 36:48.607
I have seen the worst images

36:48.640 --> 36:50.609
flooding in.

36:50.642 --> 36:51.943
All day.

36:51.977 --> 36:55.881
Every day.

36:55.914 --> 36:56.982
The solution...

36:57.015 --> 36:58.984
isn't removing...

36:59.017 --> 37:01.520
what gets posted.

37:01.553 --> 37:03.489
It's preventing people
from violating

37:03.522 --> 37:05.691
the five abuse standards
in the first place.

37:05.724 --> 37:07.926
Sending a clear message
that such behavior

37:07.959 --> 37:09.761
will not be tolerated!

37:09.795 --> 37:11.597
Sasha...

37:11.630 --> 37:13.399
what you saw was terrible.

37:14.933 --> 37:17.503
You need help.

37:17.536 --> 37:19.538
Drop that gun.

37:19.571 --> 37:21.573
I can help you.

37:22.808 --> 37:24.810
You're right.

37:26.945 --> 37:28.947
You can help me.

37:31.817 --> 37:34.653
By making sure
my message gets heard.

37:37.689 --> 37:38.790
Sasha, no, no!

37:38.824 --> 37:40.292
(gunshot)
(echoing): No!

37:44.430 --> 37:45.431
(body thuds)

37:49.601 --> 37:50.969
(indistinct police
radio communication)

37:52.471 --> 37:54.940
MUNDO:
She's wearing a QR code.

37:54.973 --> 37:58.477
Her plan was to die all along.

37:58.510 --> 37:59.978
Kill Toby Allen,
then kill herself.

38:00.011 --> 38:01.747
RYAN:
She was Violence.

38:01.780 --> 38:05.584
Sasha posted gruesome
photos of her victims.

38:05.617 --> 38:08.354
This was her fifth
and final message.

38:08.387 --> 38:11.723
Well, if there are no more
bodies, what's the QR Code for?

38:29.107 --> 38:30.342
Huh, that's weird.

38:30.376 --> 38:31.843
What do you got?
Sasha's QR code

38:31.877 --> 38:34.112
is a link to someone's
PicThread account.

38:34.145 --> 38:36.047
Click on it.

38:36.081 --> 38:37.749
KRUMITZ:
Avery, are you sure?

38:37.783 --> 38:39.985
It could blast another photo.
It won't.

38:40.018 --> 38:42.354
Whatever it links to
will be her final message.

38:42.388 --> 38:43.355
All right.

38:43.389 --> 38:44.356
(taps key)

38:44.390 --> 38:46.392
RAVEN:
It's Sasha's profile.

38:46.425 --> 38:49.027
RUSSELL:
She posted something new
ten minutes ago.

38:49.060 --> 38:51.029
How's that
possible?
Could be time-released.

38:51.062 --> 38:54.866
RUSSELL: "I died for you sins.
Keep social media clean."

38:54.900 --> 38:56.668
The press must have
leaked Sasha's name.

38:56.702 --> 38:57.769
Check out those comments.

38:57.803 --> 39:01.873
NELSON: Damn. People
are coming here to support her.

39:01.907 --> 39:04.976
Calling the DOJ about getting
this profile taken down.

39:05.977 --> 39:07.145
RUSSELL:
The last thing we need

39:07.178 --> 39:09.381
are copycats.

39:17.889 --> 39:19.858
(monitor beeping steadily)

39:19.891 --> 39:22.861
I'm happy you came to see me
at the bar.

39:24.095 --> 39:26.097
Even if you were so upset.

39:28.934 --> 39:30.936
Gave me a chance
to see Elijah again.

39:35.006 --> 39:37.609
Tragedy does really
bring people together.

39:44.916 --> 39:47.519
I had to wear a wig
to sneak in and see you.

39:47.553 --> 39:49.988
I hope you still know
it's me, Nina.

40:07.606 --> 40:08.607
Hey, Dad.
